# Implementation Plan: Pre-Launch Architecture (Studio & Reels)

This plan outlines the steps to move VibeStream from a demo phase to a production-ready ("pre-launch") state. The focus is on segregating the User and Creator experiences, implementing vertical video feeds (Reels/Shorts), and polishing the UI to an "Apple-like" premium standard while removing all mock data.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Changes Required**. We need to ensure the `videos` table can distinguish between standard videos and Shorts/Reels. We will add an `is_short` boolean flag to the `videos` table based on the aspect ratio (if height > width). Is this automatic categorization acceptable, or do you want creators to manually check a "Short" box during upload?

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Database & Schema Updates
We will add flags to support vertical video features.

#### [NEW] `setup-shorts.sql`
- Add `is_short` (BOOLEAN) to `videos` table.
- Create an index for faster querying of Shorts.

---

### 2. Creator Flow vs. User Flow (Dashboard)
We need a dedicated area for creators to manage their content, separate from the general settings page.

#### [NEW] `app/studio/dashboard/page.tsx`
- **Stats Overview**: Total views, likes, and subscribers.
- **Video Manager**: A list/table of the creator's uploaded videos.
  - Buttons to Edit (Status, Title, Description, Visibility).
  - Button to Delete video.

#### [MODIFY] [app/studio/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/page.tsx)
- Rename the current `/studio` layout to serve as a wrapper. The main content will move to `/studio/settings` (the current profile editor), and `/studio/dashboard` will be the default landing page for creators.

---

### 3. YouTube-Style Reels / Shorts Feed
A dedicated vertical feed for mobile-first consumption.

#### [NEW] [app/shorts/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/shorts/page.tsx)
- A full-screen, vertical scrolling feed (similar to TikTok/YouTube Shorts).
- Auto-playing videos with snap-scrolling.
- On-screen overlay controls (Like, Comment, Share) positioned on the right side.
- Queries only videos where `is_short` is true.

---

### 4. Profile & Channel Polish (Removing Mock Data)
The current profiles need to stop displaying placeholder videos and thumbnails, and feature a premium, Apple-like aesthetic.

#### [MODIFY] [app/profile/[username]/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/profile/%5Busername%5D/page.tsx)
- Remove all fallback/mock data generators. If a user has no videos, display a beautiful "No Content Yet" empty state.
- Refine the typography (using Inter/SF Pro patterns) and spacing to feel ultra-premium.
- Add tabs: "Videos" and "Shorts". 

#### [MODIFY] [components/VideoCard.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/VideoCard.tsx)
- Ensure thumbnails are correctly pulled from the database or R2 URL, with graceful fallbacks (not random dummy data) if the thumbnail fails to load.

---

### 7. Technical Strategy: Mobile App Separation
To compete with YouTube and Twitch, we will eventually move from a "Web App" to a native experience.

- **Phase 1 (Current)**: PWA (Progressive Web App) with native-feel gestures and bottom navigation.
- **Phase 2 (Proposed)**: Transition to **React Native** or **Capacitor**. This allows us to share 80% of our logic (Supabase, Vibe-Rank) while delivering a truly native performance on iOS/Android.
- **API First**: We will ensure all new features (Shorts, Dashboard) are built as clean API endpoints (`/api/...`) so that a separate mobile app can consume them without refactoring.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Upload a vertical video and verify it gets flagged as `is_short=true`.
- Navigate to `/shorts` and verify vertical snap-scrolling works.

### Manual Verification
- **Creator Dashboard**: Sign in, navigate to `/studio/dashboard`, edit a video title, and delete a test video. Verify changes reflect on the channel.
- **Profile Check**: View a profile with zero videos to ensure no mock data bleeds through. View a profile with videos to check the premium styling block.
